Package Licence

Class DrivingLicence

  • java.lang.Object
    • Licence.DrivingLicence

  • public final class DrivingLicence
extends java.lang.Object

    Licence.DrivingLicence

    This is a class for objects of Licence.DrivingLicence type. A driving licence object stores details about the driver including their full name, date of birth, licence number, the date their licence was issued and whether or not they hold a full licence.

    2018-02-12
